stfs
Symbolic Tagging File System
==========================
FUSE file system that uses tags instead of file names. Symlink based.


Based on what?


mkstfs [database]
===============
Create a new stfs database at the path. If the path is omitted, create it in
the current directory, at '.stfs'.

stfs [database] mount-point
===========================
Mount a stfs database at some directory. If the database path is omitted, look
for it in the current directory, at '.stfs'.
